1 Download Debian Iso From https://www.debian.org/
2 Flash Debian Iso Using Rufus dd Mode Ventoy Or BalenaEtcher
3 If You Are On Debian Installer menu I Would Recommend Selecting Install Not Graphical Install
4 If You Are On Tasksel I Would Recommend To Deselect Gnome And Debian Desktop Environment By Pressing Space On GNOME And Debian Desktop Environment just standard system utilities only then press enter
5 After You Install It Login Then enter su - then apt install sudo then sudo nano /etc/sudoers then add yourusername  ALL=(ALL:ALL) ALL Then ctrl x y enter then type exit to exit root
6 run sudo apt update && sudo apt upgrade
7 sudo apt install fastfetch
8 Run sudo nano /etc/os-release
  Then Change PRETTY_NAME="Debian GNU/Linux 13 (trixie)" To PRETTY_NAME="Adrenaline Linux"
  Then Change NAME="Debian GNU/Linux" To NAME="Adrenaline Linux"
  Then Change VERSION_ID="13" To VERSION_ID=""
  Then Change VERSION="13 (trixie)" To VERSION=""
  Then Change VERSION_CODENAME=trixie To VERSION_CODENAME=
  Then Change DEBIAN_VERSION_FULL=13.3 To DEBIAN_VERSION_FULL=
  Then Change ID=debian to ID=adrenaline
  Then Change HOME_URL="https://www.debian.org/" To HOME_URL="https://github.com/Haikal02-alt/Adrenaline-Linux"
9 Then Run sudo nano /etc/issue Then Change Debian GNU/Linux 13 \n \l To Adrenaline Linux \n \l
  Then Run sudo nano /etc/issue.net Then Change Debian GNU/Linux 13 To Adrenaline Linux
  Then update-grub with sudo update-grub for grub
10 run sudo nano /etc/grub.d/10_linux
   Then Change OS=GNU/Linux To OS= If You See Any OS=GNU/Linux And Also Change OS="${GRUB_DISTRIBUTOR} GNU/Linux" To OS="${GRUB_DISTRIBUTOR}" Then Find GRUB_DISABLE_SUBMENU= Then Change GRUB_DISABLE_SUBMENU="true" To GRUB_DISABLE_SUBMENU="false"
   Then Update Grub using sudo update-grub
11 Run sudo rm /usr/share/desktop-base/ceratopsian-theme/grub/grub-4x3.png
   Then sudo rm /usr/share/desktop-base/ceratopsian-theme/grub/grub-16x9.png

11 Have Fun And Start Using This OS
